#### API Summary

#### User Information
* [ReadUserState](#capi-playerstate-readuserstate) - Read the state of the currently logged in user. Optional parameter: entityTypeFilter
* [UpdateUserName](#capi-playerstate-updateusername) - Update User name.
* [UpdateContactEmail](#capi-playerstate-updatecontactemail) - Update contact email.
* [UpdateUserPictureUrl](#capi-playerstate-updateuserpictureurl) - Update user picture URL.
* [UpdateLanguageCode](#capi-playerstate-updatelanguagecode) - Update's user language preference.
* [UpdateTimeZoneOffset](#capi-playerstate-updatetimezoneoffset) - Update's user timezone offset.
* [UpdateSummaryFriendData](#capi-playerstate-updatesummaryfrienddata) - Update summary friend data.
* [UpdateIsTester](#capi-playerstate-updateistester) - Update flag indicating player is a tester or not.

#### Attributes
* [GetAttributes](#capi-playerstate-getattributes) - Get player attributes.
* [UpdateAttributes](#capi-playerstate-updateattributes) - Update player attributes.
* [RemoveAttributes](#capi-playerstate-removeattributes) - Remove player attributes.

#### Status
* [SetUserStatus](#capi-playerstate-setuserstatus) - Set timed status for a user
* [GetUserStatus](#capi-playerstate-getuserstatus) - Get user status
* [ExtendUserStatus](#capi-playerstate-extenduserstatus) - Extend user's status
* [ClearUserStatus](#capi-playerstate-clearuserstatus) - Deletes the specified status

#### Management
* [Logout](#capi-playerstate-logout) - Logs player out of the server.
* [ResetUser](#capi-playerstate-resetuser) - Deletes the data owned by the user but does not delete the user itself.
* [DeleteUser](#capi-playerstate-deleteuser) - Deletes the user and data owned by the user.
* [ResendValidationEmail](#capi-playerstate-resendvalidationemail) - Resend validation email.